comment: Had the Cask strength, it was superbly balanced fruity, sweet and spiced.
Will differ based on cask batch but the one i tried had a soft sweet fruity flavour and a well controlled medium finish. I prefer the cask strength version but not a bad Australian whisky!
Lekker zoete smaak, maar erg sterk
Very plummy with a creme brulee after taste. Loved it!
